    "custom_faq_jaMpLP": {
      "type": "custom-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_pRH6Wf": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I know what degree of hearing loss I have?",
            "answer": "<p>Age-related hearing loss is progressive, and your hearing slowly gets worse over time, so it's easy to overestimate your hearing abilities. Ceretone offers a free online hearing test, allowing you to quickly and accurately assess your current degree of hearing loss.</p>",
            "opened": true
          }
        },
        "accordion_fzGb4W": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What makes these devices so affordable?",
            "answer": "<p>We are committed to providing cost-effective hearing solutions for individuals with hearing loss. Our direct-to-consumer online approach allows us to offer competitive pricing without compromising quality or service. As a result, our hearing aids are priced significantly lower than traditional hearing aids.</p>",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_N7zeXC": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do Ceretone hearing aids compare to hearing aids from a clinic?",
            "answer": "<p>The Ceretone Core One series are professional hearing aids registered with the FDA and subject to FDA over-the-counter regulations. Ceretone is dedicated to bringing the latest technology to Americans at the lowest possible price, helping as many people as possible improve their hearing.<br>Ceretone hearing aids are generally more affordable than clinic hearing aids because they don’t require additional clinic or service fees. Additionally, Ceretone offers ongoing support anytime.</p>",
            "opened": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_4QAT9d": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I request a return if I’m not completely satisfied with Ceretone hearing aids?",
            "answer": "<p>At Ceretone, our utmost priority is your complete satisfaction. If for any reason you’re not satisfied with your Ceretone hearing aids within 60 days of purchase, you may return them for a full refund. See our full Warranty and Return Policy for details.</p>",
            "opened": false
          }
        }
      },
